    dc:description "FIGURES 39 – 40 b. Riscus austroamericanus Den Heyer & Castro sp. nov. Female. Dorsum (39 a); posteriodorsal region of idiosoma (39 b); venter (40 a); posterioventral region of idiosoma (40 b). UMB = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280750/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280751>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Riscus austroamericanus Den Heyer & Castro sp. nov. Female. Propodosomal region, dorsal view (40 a); sensillum vi (41 b); sensillum sce (41 c). UMB = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280751/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280752>
    dc:description "FIGURES 42 – 48. Riscus austroamericanus Den Heyer & Castro sp. nov. Female. Genital valve (42) Hypognathum (43); Palp (44); leg I (45 a & b); leg II (46); leg III (47); leg IV (48). UMB = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280752/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

